@{b}Contents.........@{ub} 600 Amiga fonts, 670 Adobe Type 1 PostScript
                  fonts (.pfb and .afm files only, shareware),
                  670 Compugraphic fonts, 1200 EPS images,
                  1800 black & white IFF images, 24 Amiga
